"Eco for CA Foundation is India’s First comprehensive app for Economics & Business Commercial Knowledge for CA Foundation as well as CA CPT as per the syllabus and guidelines by Institute of Chartered Accountants of India (ICAI) .This comprehensive app is regularly Managed, Updated, Designed and Developed by CA Deepak Mulchandani, a renowned faculty in Business Economics, Business Commercial Knowledge, Strategic Management & Economics For finance for students so that students may practice Mock Test Series with Real-Time Answers, Exam Timer and Graphical Results, helping them adapt to CA Foundation Exam Environment.
It is generally seen that a CA Foundation & CA CPT student faces oodles of difficulties while going through the ICAI study material. This happens because of its typical language and cumbersome presentation. So many students get scared seeing the size of the ICAI material. To overcome the lack of intuitive design and simplicity, Eco & BCK for CA Foundation App brings you a one-stop app that has everything you need to prepare for Economics &Business Commercial Knowledge Exam for CA Foundation as well as CA-CPT.
Eco for CA Foundation (Chartered Accountancy – Entrance Test) Android App makes it easier and more intuitive to study for CA Foundation with the following Advantages: 
* Mock Test Series with Real-Time Answers, Exam Timer and Graphical Results for CA Foundation. * Latest Notifications, Updates and IMP alerts for upcoming CA Foundation exams and results for Various Subjects including (But not limited to) Economics For Finance , Strategic Management (SM) .
* FAQ's and Articles, Tips and Strategies for Exam Preparation of Economics & Business Commercial Knowledge for CA Foundation exam. * Daily updates, Revision Notes, Test Papers, Case Studies and Online Questionnaire of CA Foundation Curriculum.
* Placement List Updates so that you never lose track of upcoming job opportunities.
*One-Touch Access to Video and Classroom Lectures from Nahata Professional Academy by CA. Deepak Mulchandani.
* Including daily updates related to Self Grooming, Personality Development, Motivation, HR Interview as well as miscellaneous Tips by CA Deepak Mulchandani to build your Corporate Personality as per the Profile and Industry Standards requirement sought by the World’s Best CA FIrms.
*Easy Signup via Facebook for convenience

This Application is beneficial for CA-CPT students for their self assessment & Improvement in economics. This will is designed to thoroughly guide students to score good marks in your exams particularly in Economics.

We hope that you will like the application and also wish you Best of Luck for your future."
